QL, AWS\n\nBias for action: Startup mentality, get things done, fast iterations, scope and implement project-level solutions with minimal guidance, strong problem-solving and decision-making capabilities. Previous experience in a small startup (or as a founder) is highly preferred.\n\nCuriosity and Continuous Learning: You are up to speed on developments in fullstack technologies and patterns, and constantly thinking about how to apply new technologies and offerings to our platform.\n\nDesire to Improve: You seek to understand why things are the way they are, and think about ways to make them better.\n\nProduct Sense: You seek to understand the features you're working on, and actively propose positive changes. Collaborate with product and design to inform roadmap decisions.\n\nTeam Player: You have excellent communication skills (verbal and written), enjoy collaborating with others and mentoring team members.\n\nDeliver Legendary Customer Experience: You have experience building and scaling products that delight real users.\n\nOwnership: Strong sense of ownership and accountability, honor commitments and be transparent about challenges.\n\nJob Location\nThis position is available in the United States and Canada.\nWe are a remote-first company so youΓÇÖll be working from home most of the time, traveling for in person sessions a few times a year.\n\n\nThe estimated total compensation for this role is $180,000 - $220,000 per year.\n\nReady to join our team and have a tremendous impact? WeΓÇÖd love to hear from you. Also, we know itΓÇÖs tough, but please try to avoid the ΓÇïΓÇïconfidence gapΓÇï.ΓÇïΓÇï You donΓÇÖt have to match all the listed requirements exactly to be considered for this role.\n\nApply\nFirst Name *\n\nLast Name *\n\nEmail *\n\nRequired\n\nLinkedIn Profile URL *\n\nPhone Number\n\nDo you require Visa sponsorship to work in the US or Canada? *\nYes\nNo\nResume *\nDrag and drop files or browse computer\n(PDF only, 5 MB maximum)\nAuto-fill candidate info from their resume\nApply\nJobs powered by\nDover Logo\nConveyor is compliant with AI Employment Regulation	1
