\nZipRecruiter.org\nZipRecruiter UK\nLogos provided by Clearbit\nYour privacy is our priority. Learn more: Your Privacy Choices\n\nPrivacy Policy\nCalifornia Privacy Notice\nTerms of Use\nCookie Policy\nAttribution Notices\nCorporate Responsibility\nSecurity and Compliance\nZipRecruiter, Inc. ┬⌐ 2026 All Rights Reserved Worldwide\n\n\n\n\nBack to Home\nWordPress Developer (Remote)\nAlpha Imprint LLC\nHouston, TX ΓÇó Remote\n\n\n1-Click Apply\n\n\n$80K - $90K/yr\n\nFull-time\n\nPosted yesterday\n\nBe Seen First\n\nAfter you apply to this job, you can share why youΓÇÖre interested to jump to the top of the candidate list.\n\nJob description\nWeΓÇÖre looking for a Remote WordPress Developer who can take full ownership of our marketing website, from building pixel-perfect landing pages to maintaining strong site performance.\n\nYouΓÇÖll work closely with our marketing, design, and SEO teams to launch impactful features and improvements that help Alpha Imprint stay competitive online.\n\n \n\nAbout Us\n\nAlpha Imprint helps businesses elevate their brand through high-quality promotional products, branded apparel, trade show signage, and professional printing solutions. We partner with companies across the U.S. to create memorable brand experiences through customized merchandise, signage for events and trade shows, and premium print materials.\n\nAs our online presence continues to expand, weΓÇÖre looking for a skilled WordPress developer who can help us create fast, modern, and high-performing web experiences.\n\n \n\nWhat YouΓÇÖll Do\n\nCreate high-converting landing pages that precisely follow provided UI/UX designs.\nDevelop and launch new site components, including templates, custom post types, Gutenberg blocks, and ACF field structures.\nIdentify and resolve issues reported in Google Search Console such as crawl errors, indexing problems, schema issues, and security warnings.\nImprove site speed and Core Web Vitals by auditing plugins, implementing critical CSS strategies, and optimizing image/CDN usage.\nSet up and maintain deployment workflows using tools like CI/CD pipelines, GitHub Actions, WP-CLI, Bedrock, or similar solutions.\nCollaborate regularly with designers and copywriters using tools such as Figma, Slack, and Loom.\n \n\nRequired Qualifications\n\nAt least 2 years of professional experience developing WordPress sites, including custom themes or plugins.\nDemonstrated experience improving Core Web Vitals on live websites (please provide before/after examples).\nStrong skills in PHP, modern JavaScript (ES6+), and SCSS or Tailwind, with experience developing Gutenberg blocks.\nSolid understanding of technical SEO, including Google Search Console, schema markup, sitemaps, robots.txt, and redirects.\nComfortable working with Git workflows, automated testing, and accessibility standards such as WCAG 2.1 AA.\nStrong written and spoken English, with availability for roughly 3 hours of overlap with U.S. Central Time.\n \n\nNice-to-Have\n\nExperience working with WooCommerce or headless WordPress architectures using REST APIs or GraphQL.\nFamiliarity with integrations related to Salesforce, HubSpot, or marketing automation platforms.\nBasic design awareness and the ability to navigate Figma and communicate effectively with designers.\n \n\nPerks & Benefits\n\nFully remote position with flexible working hours.\nPerformance-based bonus opportunities.\nHardware or learning stipend for professional growth.\nPaid vacation, holidays, and sick leave.\n \n\nHow to Apply (Read Carefully ΓÇô This Is Your First Test) ΓÜá∩╕Å\n\nWe only review applications submitted through our website. Please follow the steps below:\n\nSearch for ΓÇ£Alpha ImprintΓÇ¥ on Google.\nVisit our website and navigate to the About Us section. Choose the button labeled as ΓÇ£Join Alpha!ΓÇ¥.\nComplete the application form\n \n\nΓÜá∩╕Å Applications submitted through our website will receive priority consideration. ΓÜá∩╕Å\n\nWeΓÇÖre looking for someone who pays attention to details and can follow instructions.\n\nWeΓÇÖre excited to meet the WordPress expert who will help us create digital experiences that support the brands we work with!}\n\n \n\nCompany Description\nAlpha Imprint provides promotional products, branded apparel, trade show signage, and custom printing services for businesses across the United States. Our team helps organizations strengthen their brand visibility with high-quality merchandise, expert customization, and dependable service.\n\nReport	3
