ng RabbitMQ or Kafka\nContribute to React + TypeScript UI features (forms, workflows, dashboards)\nDebug and resolve issues in distributed, message-driven systems\nWrite automated tests and participate in code reviews\nCollaborate with product, design, and senior engineers in an agile environment\n\n\nQualifications:\n\n3+ years of experience developing backend services using .NET (Core 5+) and C#, including profiling and optimizing code\n2+ years of experience building and/or maintaining UIs in React.js, TypeScript, and browser JavaScript. Experience with Node.js (using yarn or NPM) a plus.\nHands-on production experience building or maintaining microservices\nProduction experience with RabbitMQ or Kafka (publishing, consuming, or supporting asynchronous workflows)\nExperience using Node.js (tooling, build processes, or lightweight services)\nExperience building RESTful APIs and working with JSON. Exposure to GraphQL and YAMP a plus.\nWorking knowledge of MongoDB (queries and basic indexing)\nExperience writing automated tests (xUnit/NUnit for C#, Jest/Mocha for JavaScript)\nExperience using Git in a team environment (branches, pull requests)\nBachelorΓÇÖs degree in a technical field (e.g., Computer Science) or equivalent experience preferred\nExperience with MS Azure preferred\nWilling and able to travel once per quarter to the corporate office in central FL for team collaboration and training required. Travel expenses paid by the company.\n\n\nWhat This Role Is Not:\n\nNot a senior or architect position\nNot responsible for system-wide architecture decisions\nNot a DevOps-only or frontend-only role\nNot a ΓÇ£list every technology youΓÇÖve ever touchedΓÇ¥ position\nWe value real production experience, honesty, and depth over buzzwords.\n\nCompany Description\nEnterprise Recruiting Company is a full-service talent acquisition and consulting company specializing in the areas of IT/Tech, HR, Accounting/Finance, Private Equity, Sales & Marketing, Operations and Engineering & Construction.\n\nReport\n\nEnterprise Recruiting logo\nAbout Enterprise Recruiting\nIndustry\nMedical equipment and supplies manufacturing\n\nCompany size\n1 - 10 Employees\n\nHeadquarters location\nCarlsbad, CA, US\n\nYear founded\n2003\n\nWebsite\nenterpriserecruiting.net\nView All Enterprise Recruiting Jobs	3
